HEADWORD: Ominate
<hw>Om"i*nate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t. & i.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>ominatus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>ominari</ets> to presage, fr.
<ets>omen</ets>.]</ety> <def>To presage; to foreshow; to
foretoken.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Dr. H. More.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
